data.text: A daughter is someone you laugh with dream with and love with all your heart
May you forever sparkle and shine like the star that you are Happy birthday my princess
Happy birthday my daughter May your day be as bright as your smile and as lovely as you
A daughter is just a little girl who grows up to be your best friend
Happy birthday to my darling daughter You are unbelievably precious to me
I hope you realize that you are my everything May your birthday be filled with splendor and love
You are such a positive charming and absolutely adorable daughter
The more a daughter knows the details of her mothers life the stronger the daughter
I am so fortunate that I was blessed with a wonderful daughter like you
I hope your special day is just as sweet as you are Happy birthday
Daughters are like flowers they fill the world with beauty and sometimes attract pests
You are such a treasure not only to me but to our whole family Happy birthday to our precious gem of a daughter
You light up the world around you and you continually dazzle me with your love
May your birthday sparkle just as much as you do
May your birthday herald the beginning of an astounding life for you
Daughters are like flowers that fill the world with beauty
I hope your birthday is filled with joy and love Happy birthday to my little daughter
I hope your year is as stupendous as you are happy birthday to my princess
Beloved daughter, I wish you a long and happy life
We always pray for you that you get everything in your life dear dauther
Thanks for making us proud every day. Wishing you a very joyous and happy birthday
Happy Birthday to the most wonderful daughter in the whole world
Happy birthday, lovely daughter May your big day be as wonderful and adorable as you are
On her special day, I hope and pray that all her dreams come true
We are proud that we got a charming princess as our daughter. Happy birthday to our beautiful angel.
